  <num>19-1704.05</num>
  <heading proof="needed">Power to contract: presently exercisable power of appointment.</heading>
  <para>
    <num undesignated="true">(a)</num>
    <text>A powerholder of a presently exercisable power of appointment may contract:</text>
    <para>
      <num>(1)</num>
      <text>Not to exercise the power; or</text>
    </para>
    <para>
      <num>(2)</num>
      <text>To exercise the power if the contract when made does not confer a benefit on an impermissible appointee.</text>
    </para>
  </para>
